        "display_order": 109,
        "code": "desi-dsk",
        "label": "Digital skills",
        "alt_label": "Digital skills",
        "definition": "<p>The digital skills group of indicators assesses both internet user skills of citizens and the number of specialists with advanced digital skills. At least basic digital skills and ICT specialists measure targets of the Digital Decade Policy Programme.</p>",
        "parent": [
            "dd_people"
        ],
        "colors": "[]",
        "icon": ""
    }
},
{
    "model": "core.indicatorgroup",
    "fields": {
        "created_at": "2023-09-29T13:39:36.611Z",
        "updated_at": "2026-04-08T06:59:28.303Z",
        "display_order": 111,
        "code": "desi-infra",
        "label": "Fixed and mobile infrastructure",
        "alt_label": "Fixed and mobile infrastructure",
        "definition": "<p>Under this group of indicators, both fixed and mobile broadband are analysed with indicators measuring the supply and the demand side. Fixed VHCN and 5G coverage measure targets of the Digital Decade Policy Programme.</p>",
        "parent": [
            "dd_infra"
        ],
        "colors": "[]",
        "icon": ""
    }
},
{
    "model": "core.indicatorgroup",
    "fields": {
        "created_at": "2023-09-29T13:41:42.059Z",
        "updated_at": "2026-04-08T06:59:49.466Z",
        "display_order": 112,
        "code": "desi-dtb",
        "label": "Digital transformation of businesses",
        "alt_label": "Digital transformation of businesses",
        "definition": "<p>The Digital transformation of businesses group of indicators is made up of 3 sub-groups: digital intensity, take-up of selected technologies by enterprises and e-commerce. SMEs with at least a basic level of digital intensity, take-up of Big data, Cloud and AI are targets of the Digital Decade Policy Programme.</p>",
        "parent": [
            "dd_business"
        ],
        "colors": "[]",
        "icon": ""
    }
},
{
    "model": "core.indicatorgroup",
    "fields": {
        "created_at": "2023-09-29T13:43:48.847Z",
        "updated_at": "2026-04-08T07:00:06.860Z",
        "display_order": 115,
        "code": "desi-dps",
        "label": "Digitalisation of public services",
        "alt_label": "Digitalisation of public services",
        "definition": "<p>The digitalisation of public services group of indicators describes the demand and supply of e-government as well as e-health. The Digital public services for citizens and businesses and the access to e-health records are indicators assessing targets of the Digital Decade Policy Programme.</p>",
        "parent": [
            "dd_public_service"
        ],
        "colors": "[]",
        "icon": ""
    }
},
